uid MHD models predict that the\nresistive plasma response to the applied MP is shielded.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Apr 2018 12:39:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Jun 2018 13:17:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 29 Jun 2018 07:01:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-01"}
